				<div class="entry-content">
				<p><a href="http://urbanhonking.com/hotknives/files/2011/03/IMGP0489.jpg"><img src="http://urbanhonking.com/hotknives/files/2011/03/IMGP0489-e1301177789338.jpg" alt="" title="IMGP0489" width="500" height="343" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1416" /></a></p>
