					<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
								<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://urbanhonking.com/hotknives/2010/12/01/real-beer-buzz/#comments" title="Comment on Real Beer Buzz">3 Comments</a></span>
							</div><!-- .entry-utility -->
		</div><!-- #post-## -->

		
	

